title: Flight Simulator 2020 - POI's - Norway - Helgeland Bridge
description:
In this video we will fly over the Helgeland Bridge. The Helgeland Bridge (Norwegian: Helgelandsbrua) is a cable-stayed bridge that crosses the Leirfjorden between the mainland (in Leirfjord Municipality) and the island of Alsta (in Alstahaug Municipality) in Nordland county, Norway.
